@startuml
title HeroAircraft 单例模式结构图

class AbstractAircraft {
    + shoot() : List<BaseBullet>
}

class HeroAircraft {
    - instance : HeroAircraft
    - HeroAircraft(locationX:int, locationY:int, speedX:int, speedY:int, hp:int)
    + init(locationX:int, locationY:int, speedX:int, speedY:int, hp:int) : void
    + getInstance() : HeroAircraft
    + shoot() : List<BaseBullet>
}

AbstractAircraft <|-- HeroAircraft

note right of HeroAircraft
1. instance 为唯一实例
2. 构造方法私有
3. 通过 getInstance() 获取对象
4. init() 用于首次初始化
end note

@enduml